Concurrency Control Framework (CCF)
===================================

Setting up development environment:
-----------------------------------
  1. Clone the git repository
  2. Configure JVM  
  3. ./sbt update   (fetches dependencies)
  4. ./sbt test     (runs all tests)

Creating library package:
-------------------------
  ./sbt package

  This will produce the package to:
    ./ccf/target/ccf-{version}.jar

Running the test application:
-----------------------------
  ./sbt -p app run -s    (starts the server)
  ./sbt -p app run       (starts the client)
